🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept value of n and display all odd numbers from 1 to n.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE odd_numbers(n INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    i INT;
BEGIN
    FOR i IN 1..n LOOP
        IF i % 2 <> 0 THEN
            RAISE NOTICE '%', i;
        END IF;
    END LOOP;
END;
$$;


